Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:06.03,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, do you have everything?}Chủ nhân, ngài có quên gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:07.98,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I'm good.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:11.99,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, are you sure?}Ngài chắc chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.49,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I've told you over and over.}Tôi nói bao nhiêu lần rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:16.65,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't need you to see me out.}Không cần phải đưa đi đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:20.41,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But it's quite dangerous these days.}Nhưng bên ngoài nguy hiểm lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:21.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Besides...}Hơn nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.52,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'll be okay. Really.}Đã nói là không sao rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:25.99,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Just watch the house for me, Lilith.}Cô ở nhà trông nhà đi Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:27.07,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:28.59,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Got it?}Được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.70,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:36.03,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Okay, I'll be going.}Vậy tôi đi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:37.65,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:40.49,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Your necktie is loose.}Cà vạt lỏng kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:42.37,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Th-Thanks.}C-Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.07,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{There's dust on your shoe.}Giày có bụi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:49.82,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Maybe the other outfit \Nwould have been better...}Hay là thay bộ khác nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:51.96,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Your hair...}Tóc của chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:53.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Your sleeves...}Tay áo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:57.94,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What's the matter, young master?}Có chuyện gì vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:08.18,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Are you so charmed by me that \Nyou don't want to go to school?}Không lẽ tôi quyến rũ quá nên \Nngài không muốn đi học nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.87,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No... It's just that it's like we're married.}Không... chỉ là chúng ta như vợ chồng mới cưới.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:15.85,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{My mom did the same things \Nfor my dad every day.}Mẹ tôi cũng hay làm thế cho ba tôi mỗi ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:18.46,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{They were really lovey-dovey.}Họ rất là quấn quýt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:20.49,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{L-Love-dovey?}Q-Quấn quýt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:28.64,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Y-Young master, you're going \Nto be late for school.}Chủ nhân, ngài sẽ muộn học đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:30.74,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, right.}À phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:32.22,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'll see you later.}Gặp sau nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:37.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Off you go.}Ngài đi cẩn thận.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:55.30,Show_Title - Sus Maid,,0,0,0,,{\fad(3175,0)}{The }{\fs40\c&H953CA0&}{Maid }{\c\fs}{I Hired Recently\NIs }{\fs40\c&H953CA0&}{Mysterious}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:22.46,Ep_Title - Sus Maid,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{Episode 3:}{\fscx125\fsp2}{     Gojouin Tsukasa Is Precocious}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.39,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Fujisaki.}Cảm ơn Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.73,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Off you go, young lady.}Cô chủ đi cẩn thận.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.70,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san...}Yuuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:55.74,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I heard from Fujisaki that \Nhis parents passed away.}Mình nghe Fujisaki nói ba mẹ cậu ấy đã qua đời.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:57.97,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{He doesn't seem to have recovered.}Trông vẫn chưa ổn lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:03.12,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm late, thanks to Lilith.}Nhờ Lilith mà mình đi trễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:08.42,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Mình đã ra lệnh rồi.\
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.69,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She should be all right.}Chắc sẽ ổn thôi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.37,Main,Student E,0,0,0,,{Hey, have you heard?}Nè, nghe gì chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.80,Main,Student F,0,0,0,,{What?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.21,Main,Student E,0,0,0,,{Didn't you know?}Không biết gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.94,Main,Student E,0,0,0,,{His parents died in an accident.}Ba mẹ cậu ấy qua đời do tai nạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:24.67,Main,Student F,0,0,0,,{Seriously?}Thật sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:27.77,Main,Student E,0,0,0,,{His servants all quit, too.}Tất cả người hầu cũng nghỉ luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:31.18,Main,Student F,0,0,0,,{So is he living on his own?}Vậy cậu ta đang sống một mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.59,Main,Student F,0,0,0,,{What's he going to do?}Cậu ấy sẽ ra sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.59,Main,Student E,0,0,0,,{Dunno.}Ai biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.72,Main,Student E,0,0,0,,{I heard it's pretty bad.}Nghe nói tệ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.54,Main,Student E,0,0,0,,{I wonder if he can afford tuition.}Có trả nổi tiền học không nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.12,Main,Student C,0,0,0,,{Hey, cut it out.}Này đừng nói nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:41.41,Main,Student D,0,0,0,,{Yeah. That's mean.}Phải đó, vừa thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.97,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san...}Yuuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.40,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Good evening.}Chào buổi tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.05,Flashback - Sus Maid,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{G-Good evening.}C-Chào buổi tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.23,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{There's a boy at my school, in my class,}Cậu bạn học cùng lớp, cùng trường mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:05.27,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{that I remember for his honest eyes.}người có cặp mắt trung thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:10.86,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{He spoke to me, even though \NI'm so timid and quiet.}Cậu ấy đã bắt chuyện dù mình luôn im lặng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:12.47,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{It made me very happy.}Nó khiến mình rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.05,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Maybe it's presumptuous of me,}Tuy có thể phiền hà,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:21.59,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{but if there's anything I can do, \NI'd like to help him.}nhưng nếu có gì được mình sẽ giúp cậu ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.45,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Be brave, Tsukasa.}Vững vàng lên Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.95,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{U-Um, Yuuri-sa—}Yuuri nè--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.92,Main,Sensei,0,0,0,,{Okay, everyone. Take your sea\ts, please.}Mọi người về chỗ ngồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.56,Main,Students,0,0,0,,{Yes, ma'am.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:47.14,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I wonder why the young \Nmaster is so resistant.}Không biết sao chủ nhân lại không thích nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:53.81,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is it because he doesn't trust \Nmy capabilities as a maid yet}Hãy vẫn chưa tin tưởng mình là một hầu gái thực thụ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.70,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{No, I can't keep moping.}Không, không được buồn bã.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:05.67,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I have to work hard so he'll \Naccept me as soon as possible.}Phải thật chăm chỉ để chủ nhân công nhận mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:10.92,Main,Student C,0,0,0,,{Hey, where did you go for summer break?}Nè hè này cậu đi đâu vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:14.42,Main,Student B,0,0,0,,{I went to my grandfather's vacation home.}Tớ đi nghỉ mát với ông.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:16.97,Main,Student E,0,0,0,,{I went to the sea.}Tớ thì đi biển.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:19.13,Main,Student E,0,0,0,,{I rode in a huge boat.}Tớ lên một con tàu sang trọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.31,Main,Student F,0,0,0,,{Lucky.}Sướng ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.80,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{U-Um, Yuuri-san—}Yuuri nè--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.38,Main,Student G,0,0,0,,{Did you go anywhere, Tsukasa-chan?}Cậu có đi đâu không Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.50,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thank you for the meal.}Cảm ơn vì bữa ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.89,Main,Student G,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:44.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I think dinner today will be Hamburg \Nsteaks, salad, and corn soup.}Bữa tối nay sẽ là burger bò, salad và súp ngô.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.77,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yeah, that'll do.}Ừm, quyết vậy đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:50.03,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Now, I just need to go \Npick up the young master.}Giờ thì đến đón chủ nhân thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:55.88,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{He may be upset with me, but as his maid,}Có thể ngài ấy sẽ giận nhưng với tư cách là hầu gái,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:58.78,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{welcoming him home is part of my job.}mình sẽ phải thực hiện nhiệm vụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:04.39,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Piano lessons at 3 PM.}Giờ học đàn vào 3 giờ chiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.50,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{English at 5 PM.}Tiếng anh 5 giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.18,Italics,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Isn't that...}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.20,Main,Students,0,0,0,,{See you tomorrow.}Gặp sau nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.11,Main,Students,0,0,0,,{Bye.}Chào nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.13,Main,Students,0,0,0,,{Wait for me.}Chờ tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.26,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I can get home by myself.}Mình có thể tự về một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.62,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't need anyone to come take me home.}Không cần ai đón cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.73,Main,Male Student A,0,0,0,,{Whoa, what a pretty maid.}Hầu gái đẹp ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.97,Main,Male Student B,0,0,0,,{Which mansion is she from?}Phục vụ nhà nào vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:40.81,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why is Lilith here?!}T-Tại sao Lilith lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.44,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Did she come to pick me up?}Cô ta đến đón mình à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.31,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I told her so many times \Nnot to come to my school!}Đã bảo đừng đến trường rồi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:54.73,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I never got a chance to talk to him.}Cuối cùng vẫn không thể bắt chuyện...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.19,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san?}Yuuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.62,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{This is my chance!}Cơ hội của mình đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.48,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Okay, be brave, Tsukasa!}Tự tin lên Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.21,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{U-Um, Yuuri-san...}Yuuri ơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:07.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I've come to escort you home, young master.}Tôi đến đón ngài về, chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.32,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Wh-Who's that?}A-Ai thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.42,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I told you not to come to my school.}Đã bảo đừng đến rồ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.83,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm simply doing my duty as your maid.}Tôi chỉ thực hiện nghĩa vụ của mình thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:21.98,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{So the rumor about him letting \Nall his servants go was a lie.}Tin đồn người hầu nghỉ hết là sai à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.08,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{But...}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.30,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I told you...}Tôi đã nói rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.82,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{She's suspicious!}Quá mờ ám!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:36.48,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Could it be that you're embarrassed \Nabout the relationship we share?}Không lẽ chủ nhân sợ ai đó phát hiện\N ra mối quan hệ của chúng ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:42.24,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I-I-It sounds like she's talking about \Na special relationship of some sort!}S-S-Sao nghe như mối quan hệ đặc biệt vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.41,Main - Top,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's not it.}Không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.03,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{What is their relationship?!}Bọn họ là gì của nhau?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.94,Main - Top,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Tôi chỉ lo lắng thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:48.78,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Everyone's going to be mesmerized \Nif they see a beautiful maid like you!}Mọi người sẽ bị cô quyến rũ vì vẻ đẹp đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's why I don't want \Nanyone else to see you!}Thế nên tôi không muốn ai thấy cô!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I-I see.}V-Vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.38,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{He's totally flattering her!}Cậu ta hoàn toàn bị quyến rũ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:06.04,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{The maid seems to be liking it a bit, too.}Cơ mà cô hầu gái kia cũng thích...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.89,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{There's no mistake.}Không thể nhầm được!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:13.77,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{This must be a forbidden romance \Nbetween maid and master!}Là tình yêu bị ngăn cấm giữa người hầu và chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:18.95,Main - Top,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Incidentally, young master,\NI must apologize for this morning.}Với cả tôi cũng muốn xin lỗi ngài chuyện buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:19.48,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san must be in love with that maid!}Chắc chắn Yuuri đang yêu cô hầu gái đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:21.62,Main - Top,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I should have been more careful.}Tôi sẽ cẩn thận hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's fine.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.95,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's not bugging me.}Tôi không bận tâm gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:27.29,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's been a long break.}Vì kì nghỉ khá dài.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:33.21,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I thought you might want to spend \Nall your time together with me.}Nên tôi nghĩ ngài sẽ muốn bên tôi suốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:37.18,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{All... All your time together?!}C-Chỉ hai người?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:39.28,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{How lewd!}Thật đồi truỵ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:43.66,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{A man and woman mustn't be alone together!}Một người đàn ông không được\N ở riêng với một người phụ nữ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:46.51,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san is still a child!}Yuuri vẫn chỉ là đứa nhóc!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:49.52,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{The master-servant relationship, \Nthe age gap...}Mối quan hệ người hầu chủ nhân, khoảng cách tuổi tác...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.86,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{It's all so taboo!}Tất cả đều là cấm kị!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:57.19,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{But that must be exactly what \Nmakes it so passionate. I know.}Nhưng nó thật nồng cháy! Mình hiểu mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:10:00.33,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I've read a lot about it in books.}Mình đã đọc rất nhiều từ sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.06,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Of course.}Còn phải hỏi à.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:04.22,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'd love to watch over you if I can.}Nếu được tôi muốn mãi nhìn thấy cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:08.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I've been thinking about you \Nthe whole time I've been at school.}Suốt thời gian ở trường tôi chỉ toàn nghĩ đến cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.53,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I couldn't wait to see your face again.}Không thể mong chờ được gặp lại cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:15.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{If I could, I'd be with you 24 hours a day.}Nếu được tôi muốn cạnh cô 24/7.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:29.69,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{What is this throbbing in my heart?}Sao tim mình lại rộn ràng thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.51,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{It's so powerful!}Thật mạnh mẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:36.55,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san still has his honest eyes.}Yuuri vẫn giữ ánh mắt trung thực đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:40.89,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{No, his eyes when he looks at that maid...}Không, ánh mắt khi nhìn vào hầu gái đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.30,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{They're even more honest.}Chúng còn trung thực hơn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:50.15,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I was about to meddle.}Mình đã hơi lo thái quá rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:55.96,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{But I think I'd like to behold \Nthem for a while longer.}Nhưng mình sẽ quan sát họ thêm ít lâu nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.49,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Lady Tsukasa.}Tiểu thư Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:02.03,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{How long must you keep the car waiting?}Cô định để xe chờ đến bao lâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.25,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Sheesh.}Thiệt tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.62,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I've been looking for you.}Tôi tìm tiểu thư mãi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.79,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.51,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I can explain...}Tôi có thể giải thích...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.65,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, Lilith?}Sao thế Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.05,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{So it was you.}Là cô à.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's been a long time.}Đã lâu không gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Gojouin Tsukasa-sama, correct?}Tiểu thư Gojouin Tsukasa ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.36,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:34.19,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you for taking care of Master Yuuri.}Cảm ơn vì đã luôn quan tâm đến chủ nhân Yuuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.22,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{May I count on you to \Ncontinue being his friend?}Hi vọng tiểu thư có thể làm bạn với chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.47,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:42.24,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I-I look forward to it.}T-Tôi cũng muốn thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.47,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.43,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Well, then, I must be going.}Vậy tôi xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.18,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Pardon me.}Xin thứ lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:57.22,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Are you acquainted?}Người quen của cô hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:59.13,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Yes, somewhat.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:01.01,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{She's a lovely person.}Tuyệt vời nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.30,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.92,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{And so is her outfit.}Và bộ đồ cũng đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.12,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Hey, Fujisaki...}Nè Fujisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.84,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Could you wear an outfit like—}Chúng ta có thể dùng bộ đồ đó--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.42,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{If I must do that, I will quit.}Nếu thế tôi nghỉ luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{How was school, young master?}Trường học thế nào chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.10,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It was fun.}Vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.80,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lunch was delicious, too.}Bữa trưa cũng ngon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.78,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is that so?}Thế ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:23.24,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Although your cooking is still the best.}Mà tài nấu nướng của cô vẫn tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.23,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:30.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Oh, we'll be having Hamburg \Nsteaks for dinner tonight.}Tối nay chúng ta sẽ có burger bò.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.28,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.22,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That takes care of the cleaning.}Vậy là xong việc dọn dẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.45,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I haven't gone grocery \Nshopping for dinner, though.}Mình vẫn chưa mua đồ ăn tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.55,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I should hurry.}Phải nhanh lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:57.83,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm home.}Tôi về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:04.66,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.28,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.97,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She must be hiding.}Chắc đang trốn đâu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.51,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There's no point in trying to surprise me.}Lại làm mình hết hồn chứ gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.55,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Give up and come out!}Bỏ cuộc và xuất hiện đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's odd.}Lạ thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.69,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Where could she have gone?}Cô ấy đi đâu chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.09,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Shopping?}Mua sắm à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:35.90,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Well, whatever.}Mà kệ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.69,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{If she's not here...}Nếu không có ở đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.66,sign_19414_200_Potato_Chips,Text,0,0,0,,{Potato Chips}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.66,sign_19414_201_Lightly_Salted,Text,0,0,0,,{Lightly Salted}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.66,sign_19414_202_Demon_Monthly,Text,0,0,0,,{Demon Monthly}Jahy sama
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.87,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm going to enjoy being \Nalone until she gets home!}Mình sẽ tận hưởng đến khi cô ta về.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Now, then...}Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.49,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What shall I make for dinner tonight?}Tối nay làm gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.33,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's fall now,}Đã mùa thu rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.22,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{so maybe something that's in season...}Làm gì đó theo mùa chăng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:14:00.61,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Pumpkin, lotus root, sweet potato...}Bí đỏ, ngó sen, khoai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.16,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Matsutake mushrooms \Nwould be a bit expensive.}Nấm Matsutake có vẻ hơi đắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.19,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I know!}Biết rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.44,Main,Fishmonger,0,0,0,,{Welcome, welcome!}Chào mừng chào mừng!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.87,Main,Fishmonger,0,0,0,,{We have some fresh ones today!}Hôm nay nhiều cá tươi lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.65,sign_20193_213_Bass_,Text,0,0,0,,{Bass}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.65,sign_20193_214_Pigfish_,Text,0,0,0,,{Pigfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.66,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Saury is the fish to have in the fall.}Mùa thu thì ăn cá thu là chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:17.41,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll make it a full course of saury.}Hôm nay mình sẽ làm món cá thu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.83,Main,Fishmonger,0,0,0,,{Welcome!}Chào mừng!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.71,Main,Fishmonger,0,0,0,,{What'll it be, miss?}Tiểu thư cần gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.38,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{May I have some saury?}Tôi muốn mua ít cá thu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.12,Main,Fishmonger,0,0,0,,{Shucks, sorry!}Xin lỗi nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:28.60,Main,Fishmonger,0,0,0,,{I'm fresh out of saury.}Cá thu bán hết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Oh, really?}Vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.34,Main,Fishmonger,0,0,0,,{It's hard to come by lately.}Gần đây khó kiếm lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:38.02,Main,Fishmonger,0,0,0,,{And it sells out quick.}Và có là hết ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:41.24,Main,Fishmonger,0,0,0,,{I have some good bonito, though.}Tôi có ít cá ngừ nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.09,Main,Fishmonger,0,0,0,,{What do you say?}Thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.49,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{No...}À không...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:46.74,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Too bad.}Tệ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.17,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I know.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.24,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll try another shop.}Qua hàng khác xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.07,sign_21246_231_Saury,Text,0,0,0,,{Saury}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.03,sign_21293_232_Saury,Text,0,0,0,,{Saury}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.03,sign_21293_233_Sold_Out,Text,0,0,0,,{Sold Out}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:00.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{They don't have it anywhere.}Không còn ai bán.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:04.50,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Maybe I should give up and \Nmake something else today.}Hay từ bỏ và làm món khác?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:07.47,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{No.}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.09,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I can't give up.}Không được từ bỏ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:12.79,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I want the young master \Nto have a delicious meal.}Mình muốn chủ nhân có bữa tối ngon miệng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.94,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I know. I'll try the next town over.}Qua thị trấn kế bên xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:23.17,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That was entertaining.}Vui ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:27.02,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Look at the time.}Trễ thế rồi à.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:28.97,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith's taking a while.}Lilith đi hơi lâu nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:31.06,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I wonder where she went.}Cô ấy đi đâu không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:34.74,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She could at least contact me \Nif she's going to be late.}Ít ra cũng phải gọi mình chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.65,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's gotten so dark already.}Tối thế này rồi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.08,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I should hurry.}Mình phải nhanh lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:58.58,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I never noticed how quiet it is without her.}Mình chưa từng nhận ra nó thật yên tĩnh khi thiếu Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.94,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Could it be something other than shopping?}Hay không phải đi mua sắm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:04.47,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is she out for business \Nshe can't tell me about?}Ra ngoài có việc không thể nói mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:09.28,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She always leaves a note when she goes out,}Lúc nào cũng để lại ghi chú khi đi đâu mà,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.00,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{but she didn't leave one today.}nhưng lần này lại không có.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:15.69,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Her cell phone number should be in here.}Số điện thoại hẳn là ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:26.20,sign_23371_253_Young_Master,Text,0,0,0,,{Young Master}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.87,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why is her phone here?}Sao lại để điện thoại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:33.04,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I finally found some.}Cuối cùng cũng tìm thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:37.36,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Now I can make a delicious \Nmeal for the young master.}Giờ thì có thể làm món ngon cho chủ nhân rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.01,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That's right...}Phải rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.37,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's gotten pretty late.}Hơi trễ thì phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.76,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{He might be worrying about me.}Có thể ngài ấy sẽ lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:48.01,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I should contact him.}Mình nên gọi điện về.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.31,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's not here...}Không ở đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:55.78,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I may have left my phone at the mansion.}Mình để điện thoại ở nhà rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:58.47,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I should hurry home.}Phải mau về nhanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.70,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She's not coming home.}Không quay về...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:11.91,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{This is my first time being home alone \Nso late since Lilith came along.}Đây là lần đầu mình ở nhà một mình\N lâu đến thế từ sau khi Lilith đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.27,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's you.}Là mày à.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:31.87,Main,Salaryman,0,0,0,,{That's the third one.}Cái thứ 3 rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:33.47,Main,Salaryman 2,0,0,0,,{Yeah. This is bad.}Tệ thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:37.21,Main,Big Salaryman,0,0,0,,{Delays caused by train car inspections?}Tàu đến trễ do tai nạn xe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:39.07,Main,Big Salaryman,0,0,0,,{Maybe I'll go get a drink.}Đi uống vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.99,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Oh, no...}Không ổn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.70,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Now I can't get home.}Giờ mình không thể về nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.16,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Sheesh.}Thiệt tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.83,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Whatever will I do with the young lady?}Tiểu thư đúng là rắc rối.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.60,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Demanding that I go buy \Nher manga immediately...}Bắt mình đi mua manga ngay lập tức...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:58.54,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She just showed up one day out of nowhere.}Cô ta tự nhiện xuất hiện...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.60,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I shouldn't be surprised \Nif she leaves suddenly.}Nên đột nhiên biến mất cũng chẳng có gì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:05.85,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Besides, I'm better off without \Nthat suspicious maid anyway.}Mình không cần một hầu gái mờ ám như vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:14.08,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you. I owe you.}Cảm ơn cô nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:17.41,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Not at all. I just happened to be in the area.}Không có gì. Chỉ là tình cờ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:22.02,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{What were you doing in the next town over?}Cô làm gì ở thị trấn bên cạnh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Shopping for dinner.}Mua đồ cho bữa tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:27.48,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Couldn't you have bought \Nit at your local shops?}Cửa hàng ở bên mình không bán à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:28.52,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Well...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:32.02,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I couldn't find the ingredients I needed.}Tôi không tìm thấy nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.38,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.84,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{When did you get here?}Cô đến từ khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.54,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Last month.}Tháng trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:43.25,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Are you sure you want to be back here?}Không muốn quay về hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:46.01,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.44,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much.}Cảm ơn rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.94,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,Giúp đỡ nhau những lúc khó khăn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:13.11,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:24.10,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I apologize for being late, \Nand without contacting you.}Xin lỗi vì đã về trễ mà không liên lạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.63,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:33.21,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Have you cast a curse on me?}Cô đặt lời nguyền lên tôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:37.23,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{A curse to make me sad \Nwhen you aren't here?!}Lời nguyền khiến tôi buồn khi cô không ở bên?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.97,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That must be it.}Chắc chắn là thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:44.78,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I wasn't like this before you came here!}Tôi không thế này từ trước khi cô đến!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.24,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You must have!}Chắc chắn cô đã làm gì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:56.88,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Even when the mansion was so empty, \Nso dark, even when I was alone...}Dù toà nhà trống vắng, tối tăm, dù tôi có một mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.90,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I was always fine.}Tôi vẫn luôn ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:06.51,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But now, I feel so lonely and \Nisolated and anxious without you.}Nhưng bây giờ, tôi lại thấy cô đơn,\N lo lắng khi cô không ở bên.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:10.11,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What if you didn't come home?}Nhỡ cô không về thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:13.14,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I kept thinking about you \Neven more than ever.}Tôi cữ nghĩ mãi nghĩ mãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:16.09,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's such a terrible curse!}Lời nguyền thật khủng khiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:18.07,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:24.82,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{With such a curse on me, \NI can't live without you!}Với lời nguyền đó tôi không thể sống thiếu cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:38.99,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes, I did cast a curse on you,}Vâng, tôi đã nguyền rủa chủ nhân,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.36,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{so that you would become lonely.}để ngài trở nên cô đơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:45.99,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{And yet, you did well.}Nhưng ngài đã làm rất tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:48.28,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You stayed at home by yourself.}Ngài ở nhà một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:51.09,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That's my master.}Đúng là chủ nhân của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:59.29,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Don't go missing without \Ntelling me anymore.}Đừng tự ý đi mất mà không nói gì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:04.42,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Understood, young master.}Đã rõ thưa chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:51.33,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Fujisaki!}Cảm ơn Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:55.06,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I'm not your errand runner, young lady.}Tôi không phải người chạy vặt cho tiểu thư đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.23,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:01.96,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Hey, Fujisaki, could you \Nplease take a look at this?}Nè Fujisaki, cô nhìn xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:06.82,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I think you should wear this outfit!}Tôi nghĩ cô sẽ hợp với nó lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:08.32,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Come on, please?}Nè?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:11.89,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Young lady...}Tiểu thư...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:13.06,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yeah?}Sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:15.06,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I shall be leaving after today.}Tôi xin phép nghỉ ngay và luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:19.66,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I'm sure it'll look good on you!}Nó sẽ hợp với cô lắm mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:21.25,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Please! Please!}Làm ơn! Đi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:24.86,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Hey, wait! Fujisaki!}Khoan đã Fujisaki!
